Skill: Stealth Tactics
Type : Skill

Stealth tactics simply put will increase your ability to use rogue
skills that rely on stealth, such as strike and circle. Like other
tactics this skill is only useful to those who are widely versed in 
the arts of stealth.

Stealth is recieves a partial defensive and offensive boost.

To use stealth tactics, type 'stealth'. A player can only use one tactic. 

